&lt;p&gt;I remember visiting &lt;a href=&quot;https://backyardbrains.com/&quot;&gt;backyardbrains&lt;/a&gt; looking for neuroscience experiments and found a bunch of tools, blogs, experiments that I wish I had found before. I see a video lecture from the same team that makes [these things](&lt;a href=&quot;https://backyardbrains.com/products/&quot;&gt;https://backyardbrains.com/products/&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
